# 🏢 Company Website Clone

A responsive company website clone built using **HTML5** and **CSS3**. This project recreates the design and layout of a professional business website, including multiple pages such as Home, About, Services, Portfolio, Pricing, and Contact.

## 🚀 Features

* Fully responsive design
* Clean and modern user interface
* Multi-page website structure
* Service showcase section
* Portfolio/Projects section
* Pricing plans
* Contact page
* Organized file structure
* Pure HTML and CSS implementation

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
├── assets/
├── .vscode/
├── home.html
├── home.css
├── about.html
├── about.css
├── services.html
├── services.css
├── portfolio.html
├── portfolio.css
├── pricing.html
├── pricing.css
├── contact.html
├── contact.css
└── README.md
```

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3

## 📖 Pages Included

* Home
* About
* Services
* Portfolio
* Pricing
* Contact

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice and improve front-end web development skills by recreating a professional company website layout using HTML and CSS.

